*******************************************************************             
*                                                                 *             
*      @TOD  - Time of Day "MIC" Request                          *             
*                                                                 *             
*******************************************************************             
         SPACE                                                                  
@TOD     RECORD BEGIN                                                           
@TODCLK  DS    D                       Clock value                              
         END   ,                                                                
         SPACE 3                                                                
*******************************************************************             
*                                                                 *             
*      @TODBIN - Time of day "BIN" Request                        *             
*                                                                 *             
*******************************************************************             
         SPACE                                                                  
@TODBIN  RECORD BEGIN                                                           
@TODVAL  DS    D                       Clock value                              
@TODDATE DS    A                       Date area                                
@TODTIME DS    A                       Time area                                
         END   ,                                                                
